*gkrellshoot-0.3.11 (10 Jun 2002)

  29 Aug 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> * :

  Relocated to x11-plugins

  10 Jun 2002; Ben Lutgens <lamer@gentoo.org> initial commit to portage. Commit includes x11-misc/gkrellshoot, gkrellshoot-0.3.11.ebuild, ChangeLog, files, and the digest for this version. It's a neat little plugin for gkrellm with two buttons. One for locking the screen and another to snap screenshots via "import" command which is included with imagemagick. Hence the RDEPEND
